<title>bnḥṭ ḥyạtnạ qdạmk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bnḥṭ ḥyạtnạ qdạmk .. wnslm kl ạlạ̉yạm
 jạyyn lk nsẖtạq nbqy̱ lk .. kẖạrjyn mn dnyạ ạlạ̉whạm
 yạlly fy zmn ạlḥb lqytnạ .. mryt bḥyạtnạ wḥbytnạ
 wqbltnạ nbqy̱ mn sẖʿbk .. (wbdmk ạ̹nt gẖṭytnạ)2
 2- msẖ mmkn nbqy̱ lnfsynạ .. wnʿysẖ ạ̉yạmnạ wlyạlynạ
 nsẖtạq lsrạb zạỷl bạṭl .. wạ̉mạny hy msẖ lynạ
 dy ḥyạtnạ lyhạ ʿndk kẖṭẗ .. mḥfwẓẗ mn bdʾ ạlkwn
 ʿạyzyn nḥyạhạ ʿsẖạn mjdk .. (zy mạ tḥb ạ̹ḥnạ nkwn)2
 3-jhznạ jysẖ ysẖhd ʿnk .. tbqy̱ ạ̹nt mlknạ wfrḥtnạ
 wạlknz ạlly mạly qlwbnạ .. whdfnạ wkl dnytnạ
 ạ̹ksrnạ wnwrnạ bnwrk .. ʿysẖ fynạ wạ̹dynạ ḥyạtk
 ạ̹kẖfynạ wạnt ạẓhr fynạ .. (wạḥfẓnạ bs lmrḍạtk)2</lyrics>
</song>